Package: valet
Type: Package
Title: Provides R Client to the Bank of Canada's Valet API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Corey Runkel
Maintainer: Corey Runkel <runkelcorey@gmail.com>
Description: This package provides basic access to the Bank of Canada's Valet API. Work is underway to fully span the API's paths. This client defaults to wide data.frames but provides tools to access the response as a list.
